#: _posts/2026-02-19-k8s-style-CEL-with-quarkus-chicory.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It executes Wasm code within the JVM's memory space, providing a \"double sandbox\" effect (Wasm isolation + JVM\n"
"security).\n"
